### \u-10179?\u-8956? Chapter Flexibility Guidelines\par
\par
* Chapters may raise or lower thresholds based on need and member availability.\par
* L2s or L3s may act interchangeably in emergencies when qualified.\par
* If no L3 is present, L2s may form a rotating or shared anchor team.\par
* All exceptions should be logged transparently and reviewed post-mission.\par
\par
This structure offers clarity, flexibility, and a values-driven approach to leadership and contribution within SOUL.\par
