### \f2\u-10179?\u-8995?\f1  \f0 Meeting Types & Formats\par
\par
SOUL chapters are free to organize their meetings in ways that suit their needs and context. There is no required frequency or format\f1\emdash chapters may meet weekly, monthly, or seasonally, and meetings may focus on one area or combine many.\par
\par
#### \f2\u-10179?\u-9019?\f1  \f0 Common Meeting Types\par
\par
| Type              | Purpose                                                         |\par
| ----------------- | --------------------------------------------------------------- |\par
| Strategy Meeting  | Plan service missions, assign roles, and make chapter decisions |\par
| Training Meeting  | Practice skills, teach SOUL roles, and support member growth    |\par
| Social Meetup     | Bond casually through food, games, or shared conversation       |\par
| Reflection Circle | Offer emotional support, processing, and grounding              |\par
| Public Event      | Engage the wider community through service or outreach          |\par
| Media/Guest Night | Share a video, speaker, or structured discussion                |\par
\par
#### \f3\u-10179?\u-8480?\u-497?\f1  \f0 Hybrid Meeting Flow (Example Only)\par
\par
Many chapters choose to combine elements of different meeting types in a single gathering. The following flow is one example:\par
\par
1. **Arrival & Social (15\f1\endash 20 min)**: Mingling, snacks, gratitude check-in, welcoming new faces\par
2. **Strategy & Planning (30\endash 40 min)**: Discuss recent actions, proposals, and next steps\par
3. **Shared Learning (20\endash 30 min)**: Watch a video, hear a guest speaker, or share skills\par
4. **Breakout Sessions (30\endash 60 min)**:\par
\par
   * \f3\u-10179?\u-8480?\u-497?\f1  \f0 Role Training or Certification\par
   * \f2\u-10179?\u-8532?\f1  \f0 Meditation or Silent Room\par
   * \f2\u-10179?\u-9044?\f1  \f0 Conversation or Reflection Circles\par
   * \f2\u-10180?\u-8280?\f1  \f0 Creative Zone for posters, journaling, etc.\par
   * \f2\u-10180?\u-8283?\f1  \f0 Media Viewing or Extended Q\\&A\par
   * \f2\u-10178?\u-8931?\f1  \f0 Micro-Mission Planning\par
5. **Closing (10\f1\endash 15 min)**: Announcements, gratitude, optional reflection or quiet close\par
\par
#### \f2\u-10180?\u-8399?\f1  \f0 Meeting Culture\par
\par
* All participation is voluntary; no pressure to speak, meditate, or lead\par
* Leadership rotates; roles are filled by consent and availability\par
* Chapters are encouraged to adapt, remix, or evolve formats over time\par
